==Spanish==
===Noun===
'''el agua''' ''f''
: ''agua'' is a feminine noun in Spanish but, like other feminine nouns starting with a stressed ''a'' sound, it takes the masculine definite article, ''el''. It is nevertheless clearly feminine, as shown by the gender of adjectives, e.g. ''el agua clara''.

#[[water]].

